description: Welcome to vibrant and eclectic Seaport neighborhood! Step into this luminous and welcoming studio residence nestled within the coveted FP3 building. Embrace a lavish lifestyle with contemporary touches, abundant natural light streaming through expansive windows, and soaring ceilings. This spacious pied a terre showcases a cutting-edge kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances and modern cabinetry, convenient in-unit laundry, and elegant hardwood flooring throughout! Building amenities include a communal roof deck, a dynamic rotating art gallery and concierge. Enjoy the convenience of being just a brief stroll away from the hustle and bustle of Boston's Seaport District with premier shops, Trader Joes, high end cuisine and South Station public transit. just moments away.
